  "title": "Financial Advisor/Wealth Manager/Wealth Director",
  "description": "<p><strong>To apply or find out\nmore, please contact Leong Jia Wei (Reg No: R25157456) at WhatsApp +65 80358497\nor email </strong><a href=\"mailto:jiawei@placement.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jiawei@placement.com.sg</a></p><p><br />We are seeking a driven Financial Advisor/Wealth Manager to deliver comprehensive financial planning and investment advisory services to both individual and corporate clients.</p><p>The role involves evaluating clients’ financial objectives, risk profiles, and existing portfolios to recommend appropriate wealth accumulation, protection, retirement, and treasury strategies. </p><p>You will build and manage long-term relationships through regular reviews, performance updates, and proactive portfolio and cash-flow management.<br /></p><p>Looking for:</p><ol><li>Fresh Graduates (Just graduated or will be graduating in Apr-Jun ’26)</li><li>Career Switchers</li><li>PMETs</li><li>Executives & Professionals in Adjacent Industries (eg. Marketing, Sales & Events)</li><li>Options are available for senior variants of the role with appropriate remuneration.</li></ol>",
