    "description": "<p>Established in 2014, we have a proven track record in delivering successful outcomes, for candidates and for companies. By adopting a disciplined and rigorous approach to search assignments, we ensure best match, always.</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>Recognizing that having the right individual for the job is key for a company's success, our promise is to always conduct in-depth due diligence into the position requirements and to screen candidates thoroughly to assure suitability prior to presenting them for consideration.</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>Our search scope covers Permanent, Temporary or Contract Staff. In addition, we also offer Payroll Outsourcing Service and Headcount Hosting Service.</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>Have a role to fill now?&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@placement.com.sg\" target=\"_self\"><u>Send us your job description</u></a>&nbsp;and we will follow up with you shortly.</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>Looking for a job?&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@placement.com.sg\" target=\"_self\"><u>Send us you resume</u></a>&nbsp;and we will follow up with you shortly.</p>",
